author: smilek
msg: Changes to address the following JIRA issues:
JS2-701 - Package and compress the Jetspeed Desktop Javascript
Selected desktop javascript files have been renamed, changing the filename suffix from ".js" to ".src.js" so that a new compressed version of the file use the original ".js" filename.

msg: QPID-511 adjusted to use the ReadWriteThreadModel rather than setting editing the filterChain directly which could cause problems when using an InVM transport due to the way the InVM transport alters the filter chain during a connect call.
